flawed_nl_solution:
The tree drops 340 / 10 = <<340/10=43>>43 leaves for each of the four days.
Thus, it drops 43 * 4 = <<43*4=172>>172 leaves over the first four days.
Therefore, it drops 340 - 172 = <<340-172=168>>168 leaves on the fifth day.
#### 168
